OL,7,FA chemical company has been fined #2.5
OL,8,Fmillion for releasing corrosive acids
OL,9,Finto the air at its site in West
OL,10,FThurrock in Essex.
OL,12,FThe Health and Safety Executive (HSE)
OL,13,Fsaid CCTV footage showed a hydrogen
OL,14,Fchloride gas cloud engulfing the
OL,15,Fatmosphere within 60 seconds.
