OL,7,FNearby schools were closed following
OL,8,Fthe release of hydrochloric acid from
OL,9,Fthree chemical storage tanks in
OL,10,FJanuary 2020. 300,00 litres of the
OL,11,Fsubstance were released via 'poorly
OL,12,Fmaintained pipework'.
OL,14,FDue to the risk to local residents of
OL,15,Fexposure to the migrating fumes,
OL,16,Femergency responders gave advice to
OL,17,Fshut windows and doors.
