OL,7,FThe authority said: "The valve that
OL,8,Fwas designed to control leaks in the
OL,9,Fevent of cracks did not operate as
OL,10,Fintended, leading to the uncontrolled
OL,11,Frelease, increasing the risks to
OL,12,Foperators and delivery drivers.
OL,14,F"Sulphuric acid is highly corrosive
OL,15,Fand can cause lung damage if high
OL,16,Flevels are breathed in."
