OL,3,CChemical company fined #2.5 million
OL,4,Cfor releasing corrosive acids into the
OL,5,Cair
OL,7,FAn investigation by the Health and
OL,8,FSafety Executive and the Environment
OL,9,FAgency in January 2020 found that
OL,10,Fpipework had not been installed,
OL,11,Fmaintained and inspected sufficiently
OL,12,Fwhich led to several smaller pipe
OL,13,Ffailures before the more serious loss
OL,14,Fof containment.
OL,16,FIt also found that pipework had not
OL,17,Fbeen properly maintained, and a
OL,18,Fprotective chemical-resistant coating
OL,19,Fhad not been applied to the full
OL,20,Fheight of containment walls.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/9
