OL,4,Cfor releasing corrosive acids into the
OL,5,Cair
OL,7,FHSE principal inspector, Maria
OL,8,FStrangward, said: "The uncontrolled
OL,9,Frelease of significant quantities of
OL,10,Fhazardous substances in these cases
OL,11,Fwas entirely avoidable.
OL,13,F"An appropriate planned maintenance
OL,14,Fprogramme should have been in place to
OL,15,Fensure that pipes do not fail, and
OL,16,Fvalves operate. The proactive
OL,17,Fmaintenance of pipework and safety
OL,18,Fcritical valves is extremely important
OL,19,Fat sites such as these.
