OL,7,F"Industrial Chemicals Limited's West
OL,8,FThurrock site is classified as an
OL,9,Fupper tier site under the Control of
OL,10,FMajor Accident Regulations 2015, so
OL,11,Fthat businesses and communities are
OL,12,Fprotected, and potential major
OL,13,Faccidents avoided."
OL,15,FAdrian Sherman, Environment Agency
OL,16,Fregulatory officer, said: "The
OL,17,FEnvironment Agency takes its
OL,18,Fregulatory responsibilities seriously
OL,19,Fto protect communities and the
OL,20,Fenvironment.
